  ('156bcca9-b05b-f3f2-32e3-317b71834782', 'ES', 'Spain', 'olive_oils_olives', 'Aceitunas Aloreña de Málaga DOP', '["Aceitunas Aloreña de Málaga DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian table olive DOP from Málaga (Sierra de las Nieves area), distinctive split-cracked green olive cured in fennel-garlic-thyme aromatic brine. Bright green color, crisp tender flesh, balanced sweet-savory flavor with characteristic Mediterranean herbal-aromatic profile — the "split olive of Málaga".', '**Andalusian tapas centerpiece** — apéritif olive selection; with sherry; in salads; on cheese boards; signature Málaga-Costa del Sol bar olive.', '["jar-glass-200g", "jar-glass-500g", "vacuum-pack-200g", "bucket-1kg-brine", "gift-pack-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Aloreña de Málaga", "Aceituna partida de Málaga"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('c516aaf4-9c99-a20a-5eea-98e2a6cd4cb5', 'ES', 'Spain', 'olive_oils_olives', 'Aceitunas Manzanilla y Gordal Sevillanas IGP', '["Aceitunas Manzanilla y Gordal Sevillanas IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian table olive IGP from Sevilla, two distinct varieties: **Manzanilla Sevillana** (small green-bronze, classic Spanish cocktail olive, balanced sweet-savory) and **Gordal** (large bright-green, plump-fleshed, mild buttery-sweet) — Spain''s iconic table olives, the "queen olives" of tapas service worldwide.', '**Foundation of Spanish tapas service** — Manzanilla as cocktail olive (often stuffed with anchovy, pepper, almond); Gordal as premium showcase olive on tapas boards; both standard Spanish bar service.', '["jar-glass-200g", "jar-glass-350g", "jar-glass-500g", "vacuum-pack-200g", "jar-stuffed-200g", "bucket-1kg-brine", "professional-bulk-3kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Manzanilla Sevillana", "Gordal Sevillana", "Aceituna Manzanilla", "Aceituna Gordal", "Sevilla olive"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('dbfa29f8-9d9f-4faa-3829-d3a4054d2fc7', 'ES', 'Spain', 'olive_oils_olives', 'Aceitunas de Mallorca IGP', '["Aceitunas de Mallorca IGP", "Oliva de Mallorca IGP (status verify Layer 1)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Balearic Mallorcan table olive.', 'Mallorcan cuisine.', '["jar-glass-200g", "jar-glass-500g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Oliva de Mallorca"]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('f0f0f8e6-aee5-c908-1803-74a0f78b0349', 'ES', 'Spain', 'olive_oils_olives', 'Aceitunas de Verdial de Vélez-Málaga (status verify)', '["Aceitunas de Verdial de Vélez-Málaga (status verify)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('9c931a93-93b4-6f00-d7c3-53197053eae7', 'ES', 'Spain', 'olive_oils_olives', 'Aceitunas Cornezuelo de Sevilla', '["Aceitunas Cornezuelo de Sevilla", "Verdial (status verify)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('b29bd50c-f723-01ef-0ba6-bdded112012b', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón de Jabugo DOP', '["Jamón de Jabugo DOP", "Jabugo DOP", "Jamón Ibérico de Jabugo DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO", "PDO", "PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian Iberian dry-cured ham from Sierra de Aracena (Huelva), the most prestigious Iberian ham DOP. From 100% Iberian pig (or Iberian × Duroc cross) raised in dehesa (oak meadow), with Bellota grade fed exclusively on acorns during montanera season (October-February). Aged minimum 24 months, often 36-48+. Deep ruby meat with marbled golden-yellow fat (intra-muscular oleic acid from acorns, the "Pata Negra" signature), dense buttery-firm texture that melts at body temperature, intensely complex flavor: nutty-buttery base evolving to umami-savory mid-palate with sweet-floral finish, hints of dried fruit, walnut, hazelnut, oak — Spain''s most prestigious gastronomic product.', '**Premium Spanish restaurant centerpiece** — sliced very thin (almost transparent) by maestro cortador (master cutter); served at room temperature on white plate, no accompaniment; as antipasto opening for high-end menus; pairs with finos and amontillados de Jerez, Cava, premium Tempranillos.', '["whole-leg-bone-in-7-9kg", "whole-leg-boneless-vacuum-5-7kg", "hand-sliced-vacuum-100g", "hand-sliced-vacuum-80g", "pre-sliced-tray-100g", "gift-pack-sliced-200g", "professional-bulk-1kg-loncheado"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Jabugo", "Jamón de Jabugo", "Pata Negra de Jabugo", "Cinco Jotas (premium grade)", "5J"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('da6d4152-2a5e-f8ed-3e20-ce28101a155f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón de Guijuelo DOP', '["Jamón de Guijuelo DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese Iberian dry-cured ham from Salamanca (Guijuelo area), from Iberian pigs primarily (not exclusively montanera-fed; Cebo de Campo and Cebo grades common). Aged 14-30+ months. Deep ruby meat with marbled fat, dense firm texture, intensely savory flavor with characteristic salty-sweet balance, less wild-acorn-driven than Jabugo, more terroir-stable.', 'Premium Iberian ham service; very thinly sliced; pairs with Sherry and Tempranillo.', '["Same as Jabugo"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Guijuelo", "Jamón de Guijuelo", "Joselito (premium brand)", "Iberico Guijuelo"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('1494cfba-75ae-5b22-7100-e14c1a0e4160', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón Dehesa de Extremadura DOP', '["Jamón Dehesa de Extremadura DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran Iberian dry-cured ham from Badajoz-Cáceres dehesa (oak meadows), from Iberian pigs raised in dehesa with Bellota grade for premium tier. Aged 18-30+ months. Deep ruby meat with marbled fat, dense firm texture, intensely savory flavor with characteristic dehesa-acorn complexity.', 'Premium Iberian ham service; with regional cheeses (Torta del Casar); pairs with Pacharán, Sherry.', '["Same as Jabugo"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Dehesa de Extremadura", "Jamón Extremeño"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('ef29f80b-872a-81b5-40c0-9dfe508e223f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón de Los Pedroches DOP', '["Jamón de Los Pedroches DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian Iberian dry-cured ham from Córdoba province (Valle de Los Pedroches), from Iberian pigs raised in dehesa. Aged 24+ months. Deep ruby meat, dense firm texture, intensely savory with characteristic Pedroches-dehesa profile.', 'Premium Iberian ham service.', '["Same as Jabugo"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Los Pedroches", "Pedroches DOP"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('4af789e6-ea8b-5003-bcf7-174600ae4b43', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón de Teruel DOP', '["Jamón de Teruel DOP", "Paleta de Teruel DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO", "PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Aragonese dry-cured ham DOP from Teruel province, from white pigs (Landrace, Large White, Duroc — not Iberian breed). Distinctive 8-pointed-star branding, aged minimum 14 months. Pinkish-red meat with white fat, firm texture, balanced sweet-salty flavor with characteristic Teruel-mountain-aged profile — Spain''s premier white-pig (non-ibérico) DOP ham.', 'Spanish restaurant alternative to Iberian ham at lower price tier; sliced thin or hand-cut; in Aragonese cuisine; with regional bread and tomato.', '["whole-leg-bone-in-7-9kg", "whole-leg-boneless-vacuum-5-7kg", "deli-sliced-vacuum-100g", "pre-sliced-tray-150g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Teruel DOP", "Jamón de Teruel", "Paleta de Teruel (foreleg)"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('8787b8b5-4834-9eef-df70-b0edfc29ed4f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Jamón de Trevélez IGP', '["Jamón de Trevélez IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian dry-cured ham IGP from Sierra Nevada (Granada — Trevélez highest-altitude curing village in Spain). From white pigs. Aged minimum 14 months at high altitude (1,200m+) which produces distinctive sweet-floral flavor profile from cool dry mountain air; pinkish-red meat, firm texture.', 'Andalusian sierra cuisine; with regional cheeses; alternative to Iberian ham at moderate tier.', '["Same as Teruel"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Trevélez IGP", "Jamón Sierra Nevada"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('a58cefd8-8edb-e7de-ad6e-ec014bb25cd5', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Lacón Gallego IGP', '["Lacón Gallego IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Galician cured pork foreleg IGP, traditional brine-cured (not dry-cured like jamón). Pale pink meat, firm-but-tender texture (more moist than dry-cured ham), salty-savory flavor with characteristic Galician-pork profile.', '**Foundation of Lacón con grelos** (Galician national dish — boiled with turnip greens and chorizo); in pote gallego; foundation Galician winter cuisine.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-3-5kg", "half-piece-vacuum-1.5-2.5kg", "deli-cooked-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Lacón Gallego", "Galician shoulder ham", "Lacón"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('7ae1eb0c-46fe-3e87-f635-66e4feefbce9', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Cecina de León IGP', '["Cecina de León IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese cured smoked beef IGP from León province. Distinctive product — beef hindquarter cured, dried, and smoked over oak/holm-oak. Deep ruby-mahogany color, firm dense texture (denser than ham, drier), intensely savory beefy-smoky flavor — Spain''s most renowned cured beef.', 'Sliced thin for tapas, charcuterie boards (alongside Iberian hams), in salads with EVOO, in carpaccio-style preparations; pairs with Bierzo and Toro reds.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-2-4kg", "half-piece-vacuum-1-2kg", "deli-sliced-vacuum-100g", "pre-sliced-tray-100g", "gift-pack-150g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Cecina de León", "Cecina"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('29a7a685-0290-d1a2-2967-a26de85854d6', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP', '["Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Balearic Mallorcan spreadable raw-cured pork sausage IGP, distinctive paste-like texture (vs. firm sliced sausage). Made from Mallorcan black pig fat and lean, paprika (pimentón), salt, pepper. Deep red-orange color from paprika, soft creamy spreadable texture, intensely savory paprika-pork flavor — the iconic Mallorcan charcuterie product.', '**Spread on pamboli** (Mallorcan tomato bread — essential pairing); melted in cooking sauces; with honey and figs as tapa; in Mallorcan ensaïmada-savory pastry.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-300-500g", "half-piece-vacuum-200g", "jar-glass-200g", "jar-glass-300g", "professional-bulk-1kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Sobrasada de Mallorca", "Sobrasada", "Sobrassada de Mallorca (Catalan spelling)"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('de787fc4-0e1d-5a4b-fae8-bf58f8988de4', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Botillo del Bierzo IGP', '["Botillo del Bierzo IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese cured-smoked stuffed pork sausage IGP from El Bierzo (León). Made from various pork cuts (rib, tail, jaw) coarsely cut, seasoned with paprika, garlic, salt, stuffed in pork-large-intestine casing. Distinctive large irregular shape, deep red color, firm chewy texture, intensely smoky-savory pork-paprika flavor.', '**Foundation of Bierzo cuisine** — boiled with potatoes, cabbage, chorizo, in cocido berciano; classic León winter dish.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-1-1.5kg", "half-piece-vacuum-500g", "vacuum-cooked-700g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Botillo del Bierzo", "Botillo"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('935bb89b-825f-0a3a-97f9-36dc0facf510', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Chorizo Riojano IGP', '["Chorizo Riojano IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'La Rioja chorizo IGP, distinctive coiled or U-shape link, traditional preparation with pimentón (paprika), garlic, salt. Deep red color, firm texture, balanced spicy-savory paprika flavor; available dulce (sweet/mild) or picante (spicy).', 'Tapas service (sliced thin or grilled), in cocido riojano, with patatas a la riojana, in sandwiches and bocadillos; pairs with Rioja reds.', '["coiled-link-vacuum-300-500g", "individual-link-vacuum-150-250g", "pre-cooked-vacuum-300g", "deli-sliced-vacuum-100g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Chorizo de La Rioja", "Chorizo Riojano"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('f0a4dd66-e1e4-dca0-de99-07f15d59f748', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Chorizo de Cantimpalos IGP', '["Chorizo de Cantimpalos IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese chorizo IGP from Segovia (Cantimpalos), traditional dried sausage. Distinctive elongated link, deep red color from pimentón, firm dense texture, balanced spicy-savory flavor.', 'Tapas service; in cocido madrileño; with Segovian cuisine.', '["coiled-link-vacuum-300-500g", "individual-link-150-250g", "deli-sliced-vacuum-100g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Chorizo de Cantimpalos", "Cantimpalos"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('504dd162-d41e-434b-cdac-c9575122de25', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Salchichón de Vic IGP', '["Salchichón de Vic IGP", "Llonganissa de Vic IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Catalan dry-cured salami IGP from Vic (Barcelona province). Distinctive irregular long shape, white-mottled fat appearance (no paprika, classic black-pepper seasoning), firm chewy texture, balanced savory-pepper flavor — the iconic Catalan charcuterie.', '**Foundation of Catalan tapas** — sliced thin on pa amb tomàquet, on charcuterie boards, with Catalan cheeses; in fuet-style preparations.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-300-500g", "half-piece-vacuum-150g", "deli-sliced-vacuum-100g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Llonganissa de Vic", "Salchichón de Vic"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('25f557ae-50ef-7a44-de4b-bce91e1b5205', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Fuet de Cataluña', '["Fuet de Cataluña", "Fuet (status — heritage; verify Layer 1 for IGP status, Llonganissa or Fuet)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Catalan thin dry-cured pork sausage with characteristic white mold-bloom on casing. Slim cylindrical shape, mild balanced pork-pepper flavor.', 'Catalan tapas service; whole or sliced.', '["whole-piece-vacuum-150g", "twin-pack-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Fuet", "Llonganissa fuet"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('b6fbf530-c9f3-6bf5-c059-cb082b05d15f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Morcilla de Burgos IGP (proposed; verify Layer 1)', '["Morcilla de Burgos IGP (proposed; verify Layer 1)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian rice-and-blood pudding IGP from Burgos, distinctive black blood sausage with rice and onion. Deep mahogany color, soft fine texture, robust blood-pork flavor.', 'Sliced and grilled or fried in tapas service; in cocidos.', '["vacuum-pack-300-400g", "individual-link-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Morcilla de Burgos"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('68158c37-a8b5-fef0-a353-1e8ca98878f7', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Cordero de Extremadura IGP', '["Cordero de Extremadura IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran lamb IGP from regional Merina-breed flocks. Lean pink meat, delicate sweet-grass flavor.', 'Cordero al horno (roasted lamb) restaurant centerpiece; pairs with Tempranillo and Ribera del Guadiana.', '["carcass-half-10-15kg", "primal-cuts-vacuum-various", "pierna-2-3kg", "paletilla-1-1.5kg", "costillas-rack-800g-1.2kg"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Cordero de Extremadura"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('8966ea69-1b2a-4e5e-d209-d194081b409d', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Cordero Manchego IGP', '["Cordero Manchego IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Manchego lamb IGP from Manchega-breed flocks. Lean pink meat, characteristic Manchego-pasture flavor.', 'Cordero asado al horno de leña (wood-oven roast lamb) — central-Manchego restaurant signature; pairs with Valdepeñas and La Mancha reds.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6, 12]'::jsonb, '["Cordero Manchego"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('c2f8de15-8f50-a9da-cdd8-ff5a8315e1ad', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Cordero de Navarra IGP', '["Cordero de Navarra IGP", "Arkumiki Nafarroakoa IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Navarran lamb IGP from regional Lacha and Navarra-breed flocks. Lean pink meat.', 'Navarran-Basque cuisine; pairs with Navarra and Rioja reds.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Cordero de Navarra", "Arkumiki"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('514e60ce-923d-2e5c-e8b2-97248684e736', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Cordero Segureño IGP', '["Cordero Segureño IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Andalusian-Murcian lamb IGP from Sierra de Segura area, Segureña breed. Lean delicate flesh.', 'Andalusian-Murcian cuisine.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Cordero Segureño"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('61f8c802-7e0b-d76a-7dc6-d472f3a2edaf', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Lechazo de Castilla y León IGP', '["Lechazo de Castilla y León IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese suckling lamb IGP (lechazo = milk-fed lamb only, age 25-35 days, ~5-6kg carcass). Very pale tender flesh, delicate sweet milk-only flavor, fine texture — the iconic Castilian luxury lamb.', '**Lechazo asado al horno de leña** (the canonical Castilian wood-oven-roasted suckling lamb) — Segovia, Burgos, Valladolid restaurant signature; whole half lamb served family-style; pairs with Ribera del Duero and Toro reds.', '["whole-suckling-lamb-vacuum-4-6kg", "half-lamb-2-3kg", "primal-cuts-vacuum-various"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 12]'::jsonb, '["Lechazo de Castilla y León", "Lechazo", "Cordero lechal"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('7a286d05-0756-536a-619d-3e72d75b1d81', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Carne de Ávila IGP', '["Carne de Ávila IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian beef IGP from Ávila province, native Avileña-Negra Ibérica breed. Bright cherry-red meat with characteristic marbling, robust beefy flavor with grass-fed character.', '**Chuletón de Ávila** (rib eye) — Castilian steakhouse signature, grilled over wood; pairs with Ribera del Duero.', '["carcass-half-150-180kg", "primal-cuts-vacuum-various", "chuletón-1-1.5kg", "solomillo-1-1.5kg", "entrecot-300-400g", "dry-aged-pavé-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Carne de Ávila", "Avileña Negra Ibérica"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('70468d85-e5b8-f79f-2150-8da47075b45b', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Carne de Cantabria IGP', '["Carne de Cantabria IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Cantabrian beef IGP from Tudanca, Pasiega, Monchina native breeds.', 'Cantabrian regional cuisine.', '["Same as other beef IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Carne de Cantabria"]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('89073743-d680-2775-676b-6f996f8396e5', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Carne de la Sierra de Guadarrama IGP', '["Carne de la Sierra de Guadarrama IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Madrid-Sierra de Guadarrama beef IGP. Robust beefy flavor.', 'Madrid-Castilian cuisine.', '["Same as other beef IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Sierra de Guadarrama beef"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('2ddb6bfd-3950-00b8-de46-d929a430377c', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Carne de Vacuno del País Vasco', '["Carne de Vacuno del País Vasco", "Euskal Okela IGP"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Basque beef IGP, native Pirenaica and Terreña breeds. Robust flavored meat.', '**Txuleta** (rib steak) — Basque steakhouse signature, the iconic large rib-eye grilled over coals; pairs with Rioja Alavesa and Txakoli.', '["carcass-half-150-180kg", "txuleta-1.5-2kg", "dry-aged-pavé-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Euskal Okela", "Carne del País Vasco", "Txuleta vasca"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('ea5e26f4-1732-d621-6168-75a2d5d533aa', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera Asturiana IGP', '["Ternera Asturiana IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Asturian veal/beef IGP from native Asturiana de los Valles and Asturiana de la Montaña breeds. Pale-to-deep pink flesh.', 'Asturian cuisine; in cachopo (breaded stuffed veal cutlet — Asturian classic); with cabrales sauce.', '["Same as other beef/veal IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ternera Asturiana"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('84564627-2546-a24e-dfc6-0cc0f9bbf1c8', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera Gallega IGP', '["Ternera Gallega IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Galician beef IGP from native Rubia Gallega breed (and crosses). Distinctive bright reddish meat with cream-yellow marbling, characteristic Galician-pasture flavor — among Spain''s most renowned beef IGPs.', '**Premium steakhouse beef across Spain** — chuletón de buey gallego, solomillo, dry-aged for premium service; pairs with Galician and Bierzo reds.', '["carcass-half-200-300kg", "primal-cuts-vacuum-various", "chuletón-1.5-2kg", "solomillo-1.5-2kg", "entrecot-300-400g", "dry-aged-pavé-300-400g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ternera Gallega", "Rubia Gallega beef"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('99f82c95-43c4-8b44-cf40-9b5ea314c960', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera de Aliste IGP', '["Ternera de Aliste IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese veal IGP from Zamora (Aliste). Pink flavored flesh.', 'León-Zamora cuisine.', '["Same as other veal IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ternera de Aliste"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('25ade549-fc18-7442-bebf-ef6032a3e03e', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera de Navarra', '["Ternera de Navarra", "Nafarroako Aratxea IGP"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Navarran veal IGP from native Pirenaica breed. Pale pink flesh, delicate flavor.', 'Navarran-Basque cuisine.', '["Same as other veal IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ternera de Navarra"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('83c73167-63c8-7be1-9d55-3a910a28401a', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera de Extremadura IGP', '["Ternera de Extremadura IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran beef IGP from native Avileña-Negra and Retinta breeds. Robust flavored meat from dehesa-fed cattle.', 'Extremaduran cuisine.', '["Same as other beef IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ternera de Extremadura"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('92de78e1-cb68-31d0-a01a-7287c1d1bf1f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Ternera de los Pirineos Catalanes IGP', '["Ternera de los Pirineos Catalanes IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Catalan-Pyrenean veal IGP. Pink flesh, alpine-pasture flavor.', 'Catalan-Pyrenees regional cuisine.', '["Same as other veal IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Vedella dels Pirineus Catalans"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('21590e71-da67-9552-4909-8c46665d5c49', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Pollo y Capón del Prat IGP', '["Pollo y Capón del Prat IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Catalan free-range poultry IGP from Prat de Llobregat (Barcelona), distinctive blue-feet white-plumage breed. Firm flavored white-pink flesh, characteristic Catalan-poultry profile. **Capón del Prat** (capon, castrated male) — Christmas-luxury variant, larger, fattier, more tender.', 'Pollo del Prat — Catalan restaurant centerpiece; **Capón del Prat farcit** (stuffed capon) Christmas tradition; pairs with Cava and Catalan whites.', '["whole-bird-fresh-1.5-2kg", "whole-bird-fresh-3-4kg", "eviscerated-vacuum-1.5-2kg", "gift-bird-Christmas-3-5kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Pollo del Prat", "Capón del Prat", "Pota Blava (Catalan name)"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('30f84810-03e4-aa81-ce68-9781db97b6d8', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Salchichón Ibérico (status verify; likely covered under jamón ibérico DOPs as related products)', '["Salchichón Ibérico (status verify; likely covered under jamón ibérico DOPs as related products)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('bfa7bdc8-e357-dc8a-380d-964c6e591ede', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Lomo Ibérico (status verify; sub-product of jamón ibérico DOPs)', '["Lomo Ibérico (status verify; sub-product of jamón ibérico DOPs)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('6988d2ec-ec11-0a55-45b0-d6b67e5588f4', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Chorizo Ibérico (status — sub-product, status as separate IGP', '["Chorizo Ibérico (status — sub-product, status as separate IGP", "DOP varies)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PDO"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('5b70044d-1df6-2d7d-b709-6a6347494c2c', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Mortadela de Bolonia (status — likely not Spanish DOP', '["Mortadela de Bolonia (status — likely not Spanish DOP", "IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO", "PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('6ffaa4d7-180d-75ad-003b-b45d4dc440ed', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Andouille — French; not in Spain section', '["Andouille — French; not in Spain section"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('d8e350fd-8d14-d865-16bf-d6552558338e', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Espetec', '["Espetec", "Llonganissa de Catalunya (status verify)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('4a7114d0-56e8-d730-16e8-3c49b1d9f6fd', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Embotido de Salamanca (Embutidos de Guijuelo associated)', '["Embotido de Salamanca (Embutidos de Guijuelo associated)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('778403cf-1a68-cf5a-13b8-30841732370f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Embutidos de Cantimpalos (sub-products related to Chorizo de Cantimpalos)', '["Embutidos de Cantimpalos (sub-products related to Chorizo de Cantimpalos)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('c2bd49bf-c521-dc64-71c9-4f612748e394', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Patos', '["Patos", "Pichones de Tudela (status verify Layer 1 — not registered as IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('1ac191b9-2ef4-5cff-8a8f-a77ce1481cc2', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Pavo de Aragón (status verify — likely Label Calidad, not IGP)', '["Pavo de Aragón (status verify — likely Label Calidad, not IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('4868c1d1-6295-f728-825b-9368cee98f24', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Sobrassada de Menorca (status — Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP exists, Menorca separately status verify)', '["Sobrassada de Menorca (status — Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP exists, Menorca separately status verify)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('7f9e7979-ac49-456a-c6dc-663e852e8a6f', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Sobrassada Negra de Mallorca (sub-style of Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP)', '["Sobrassada Negra de Mallorca (sub-style of Sobrasada de Mallorca IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('2e2ed71f-81fe-1f92-4a0d-51dbd4547349', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Salchichón de Málaga (status verify — likely no IGP)', '["Salchichón de Málaga (status verify — likely no IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('e016d6d5-02a4-7eb7-ec06-55ecb8cf0dcc', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Llom embotit de Catalunya (status verify)', '["Llom embotit de Catalunya (status verify)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER"]'::jsonb, '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, TRUE, 'L2'),
  ('b724a5a4-cabe-bfc3-4f22-46b39c31c890', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Manchego DOP', '["Queso Manchego DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Manchego sheep''s milk pressed cheese from Manchega-breed flocks (Castilla-La Mancha). Aged minimum 30 days (semicurado) up to 12+ months (Curado, Viejo, Añejo). Distinctive zigzag esparto-grass-imprinted rind, ivory-yellow paste with small irregular eyes, firm to crumbly texture, characteristic flavor evolves from milky-buttery (semicurado) to nutty-tangy-savory with caramel notes (curado-añejo) — Spain''s most exported cheese.', '**Foundation of Spanish tabla de quesos** — sliced for tapas, cubed with membrillo (quince paste) and Marcona almonds; in tapas service across Spain; pairs with Tempranillo, Cava, and Sherry.', '["wheel-full-3kg", "wheel-full-2kg", "wheel-quarter-vacuum-700g", "wedge-vacuum-300g", "wedge-vacuum-150g", "cubed-pack-200g", "professional-bulk-aged-3kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Manchego DOP", "Queso Manchego", "Manchego Semicurado", "Manchego Curado", "Manchego Viejo"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('f7b4a078-4b82-f3db-f6c1-b40e29e66b60', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Idiazabal DOP', '["Queso Idiazabal DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Basque-Navarran sheep''s milk pressed cheese from Latxa-breed flocks. Aged 60+ days, often smoked over beech and hawthorn (the "ahumado" sub-style — most common). Pale-amber smoke-darkened rind (or natural for non-smoked), ivory-yellow paste, firm dense texture, intensely savory smoky-sheep flavor with characteristic complexity.', '**Basque tabla de quesos** centerpiece; in pintxos; with Idiazabal-stuffed empanadas; pairs with Txakoli, Rioja Alavesa.', '["wheel-full-1-3kg", "wheel-half-vacuum-500g-1.5kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g", "wedge-vacuum-150g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Idiazabal", "Queso Idiazabal", "Idiazabal Ahumado"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('4795d022-bf57-e22b-ab29-119be9b1b3d2', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Cabrales DOP', '["Queso Cabrales DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Asturian raw cow''s-or-mixed-milk blue cheese (cow milk required, sheep and/or goat optional in mix), aged in natural mountain caves of Picos de Europa. Aged 60+ days. Distinctive marbled blue-green Penicillium veining, ivory-cream paste, soft moist crumbly texture, intensely pungent salty-savory flavor with assertive blue-mineral character — among Europe''s most powerful blue cheeses.', '**Asturian tabla de quesos climax**; melted in Cabrales sauce for solomillo (steak); on toasts with sidra; pairs with **Sidra Asturiana** (canonical pairing) and Pedro Ximénez.', '["wheel-full-1-1.5kg", "wheel-half-vacuum-500g", "wedge-vacuum-200g", "crumbled-pre-pack-100g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Cabrales", "Queso de Cabrales"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('dab3ab71-75e2-cacf-7d92-3496a1226cae', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Picón Bejes-Tresviso DOP', '["Queso Picón Bejes-Tresviso DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Cantabrian raw cow''s-or-mixed-milk blue cheese DOP, aged in caves of Liébana area (Picos de Europa from Cantabrian side). Similar profile to Cabrales — assertively pungent blue-veined, intensely flavored.', 'Cantabrian-Picos de Europa cuisine; with Sidra and PX.', '["wheel-full-700g-1.5kg", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Picón Bejes-Tresviso", "Picón"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('7e99dd04-cfb1-b52e-937b-ea20a389e2c4', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Roncal DOP', '["Queso Roncal DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Navarran sheep''s milk pressed cheese from Roncal-Salazar valley flocks. Aged 4+ months. Pale ivory paste, firm dense texture, balanced sweet-nutty-tangy flavor, characteristic Pyrenean-pasture profile.', 'Navarran tabla de quesos; pairs with Garnacha de Navarra.', '["wheel-full-1.5-3kg", "wheel-half-vacuum-1kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Roncal DOP"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('0111d4cc-b43b-74f4-ca18-eee2b55978b0', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Mahón-Menorca DOP', '["Queso Mahón-Menorca DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Balearic Menorcan cow''s milk pressed cheese, distinctive square-shaped block from cloth-pressing technique, aged 21+ days for Tierno through 10+ months for Curado. Bright orange-red rind (often paprika-and-oil rubbed for Reserva), ivory paste evolving from white-cream (Tierno) to amber (Añejo), firm dense texture, characteristic salty-tangy flavor with sea-salt-air influence — distinctive Balearic terroir.', 'Mallorcan-Menorcan tabla de quesos; with regional preparations; in salads with EVOO; pairs with Cava and regional whites.', '["square-block-2-4kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g", "wedge-vacuum-150g", "cubed-pack-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Mahón-Menorca", "Queso de Mahón", "Menorcan cheese"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('545e1594-8e42-d802-fac1-d5f643b8b24a', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Tetilla DOP', '["Queso Tetilla DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Galician cow''s milk soft cheese DOP, distinctive cone/breast-shape (the name means "small breast"). Pale ivory paste, soft creamy melting texture (similar to mozzarella consistency but more mature), mild sweet-buttery flavor with characteristic Galician-milk profile.', 'Galician tabla de quesos; melted in empanadas, on tarta de queso galega; pairs with Albariño and Ribeiro whites.', '["whole-cone-500g-1kg", "half-cone-vacuum-300g", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Queixo de Tetilla", "Tetilla"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('00ea29c7-6e3c-5a78-0970-a1bc5fd79dba', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso San Simón da Costa DOP', '["Queso San Simón da Costa DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Galician cow''s milk smoked cheese DOP, distinctive elongated-pear shape, aged minimum 45 days, smoked over birch wood. Distinctive amber-mahogany smoked rind, ivory-cream paste, semi-firm texture, intensely savory smoky-buttery flavor.', 'Galician tabla de quesos; with regional preparations; pairs with Ribeira Sacra reds.', '["whole-pear-shape-400g-1.5kg", "half-piece-vacuum-300g", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["San Simón da Costa", "San Simón"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('9bf88b83-11f2-7909-267c-c3bb28862504', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso de Murcia al Vino DOP', '["Queso de Murcia al Vino DOP", "Queso Murciano al Vino DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO", "PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Murcian goat''s milk pressed cheese DOP, distinctively rinsed/bathed in Doble Pasta red wine during aging. Distinctive deep purple-red wine-stained rind, ivory paste, semi-firm to firm texture, balanced goat-milk flavor with subtle wine-tannin influence — visually striking, increasingly popular cheese.', 'Tabla de quesos visual showpiece; pairs with Murcian and La Mancha reds.', '["wheel-full-700g-2kg", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Murcia al Vino", "Murciano al Vino"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('aea1bc2d-1e84-74d6-3026-3e2028e2c266', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso de Murcia DOP', '["Queso de Murcia DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Murcian goat''s milk pressed cheese (non-wine version of Murcia al Vino), available Fresco (fresh, soft) or Curado (aged). Pale ivory color, varies from soft (Fresco) to firm (Curado), balanced goat-milk flavor.', 'Murcian tabla de quesos; with regional ensaladas.', '["wheel-full-700g-2kg", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Queso de Murcia"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('a05b7fc7-a736-bee8-071f-338e20bfd926', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso de la Serena DOP', '["Queso de la Serena DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran sheep''s milk soft pressed cheese DOP from Merina flocks (Badajoz). Aged 20+ days. Distinctive — coagulated with vegetable rennet (cardo thistle, not animal rennet), soft creamy oozing texture (often eaten with spoon when ripe), intensely savory-tangy-bitter flavor with characteristic vegetable-rennet bite.', '**Spoon-cheese service** — top sliced off, scooped with bread; on Extremaduran tabla de quesos; with regional cured meats.', '["wheel-full-700g-1kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Queso de La Serena", "La Serena"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2')
INSERT INTO gi_entries (gi_id, country_code, country, category, primary_gi_name, all_gi_names, gi_type_primary, gi_types_all, tasting_notes, horeca_use, packaging_formats, seasonal_months, aliases, is_data_thin, source_layer) VALUES
  ('0bb29c7a-b56f-b840-52c1-ca0658e6a9cb', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Torta del Casar DOP', '["Torta del Casar DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran sheep''s milk soft pressed cheese DOP from Cáceres province, similar profile to La Serena (vegetable-cardo-rennet, spoon-cheese style). Soft creamy oozing texture, intensely savory-bitter flavor — Extremaduran luxury cheese.', 'Spoon-cheese service for tabla de quesos; warmed and spooned over crusty bread; pairs with Pacharán and regional reds.', '["wheel-full-500g-1kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Torta del Casar", "Casar"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('9c5b2195-6cef-c73c-c740-e396d9175926', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso de Valdeón IGP', '["Queso de Valdeón IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese cow''s-or-mixed-milk blue cheese IGP from Picos de Europa (León side). Aged 90+ days, traditionally wrapped in maple/sycamore leaves (the "Picos de Europa" leaf-wrap signature). Marbled blue-green veining, ivory paste, semi-soft texture, robust pungent blue flavor.', 'Picos de Europa tabla de quesos; with sidra; melted in sauces.', '["wheel-full-leaf-wrapped-500g-1kg", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Valdeón", "Queso de Valdeón"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('32538c0d-61b5-5766-b16e-828118ea585d', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Ibores DOP', '["Queso Ibores DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Extremaduran goat''s milk pressed cheese DOP from Cáceres (Sierra de Las Villuercas-Ibores area). Aged minimum 60 days. Distinctive paprika-rubbed orange-red rind (or oil-rubbed), ivory paste, semi-firm texture, balanced goat-milk-paprika flavor.', 'Extremaduran tabla de quesos; with cured meats.', '["wheel-full-700g-1.2kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Ibores", "Queso Ibores"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('6a6ea428-a674-34f7-e47a-97e0bda4e2fb', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Camerano DOP', '["Queso Camerano DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'La Rioja goat''s milk pressed cheese DOP from Sierra de los Cameros. Three aged tiers (Fresco, Tierno, Curado). Ivory paste, varies firm-to-creamy by age, balanced goat-milk flavor.', 'Riojan tabla de quesos; pairs with Rioja whites and reds.', '["wheel-full-200g-1kg by tier", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Camerano"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('56a591d9-a8cd-71e9-3532-2153fd443185', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Casin DOP', '["Queso Casin DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Asturian cow''s milk pressed cheese DOP, traditional kneading-process preparation (the "amasado" technique). Distinctive flat-stamped rind, ivory paste, firm dense texture, robust pungent flavor.', 'Asturian tabla de quesos.', '["wheel-full-200-300g", "wedge-vacuum-150g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Casin", "Queso Casin"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('ab7d073b-5e72-4fd1-027c-45a936fdaffe', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Gamoneu DOP', '["Queso Gamoneu DOP", "Queso Gamonéu DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO", "PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Asturian raw mixed-milk lightly-blue cheese DOP from Picos de Europa (cow + sheep + goat mix), aged 60+ days. Distinctive pale-amber smoked rind, ivory paste with delicate blue-green veining (less assertive than Cabrales), firm semi-soft texture, complex balanced smoky-blue-mountain flavor.', 'Asturian tabla de quesos premium selection.', '["wheel-full-500g-2kg", "wedge-vacuum-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Gamonéu", "Gamoneu", "Gamonéu del Puerto (mountain style)", "Gamonéu del Valle (valley style)"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
