  ('bf68f371-7f58-3ea8-d588-8b13b1e64e51', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Queso Zamorano DOP', '["Queso Zamorano DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian-Leonese sheep''s milk pressed cheese DOP from Zamora province (Castilian sheep breeds). Aged 100+ days. Pale-amber rind, ivory paste, firm dense texture, balanced sheep-milk flavor (similar profile to Manchego).', 'Castilian tabla de quesos; alternative to Manchego.', '["wheel-full-1-4kg", "wedge-vacuum-300g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Zamorano"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('f342f60a-514f-5756-5bf7-e7c8d1da6f84', 'ES', 'Spain', 'cheeses_dairy', 'Mantequilla de Soria DOP', '["Mantequilla de Soria DOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Castilian (Soria) cow''s milk butter DOP, three styles: Natural (white-cream), Salada (salted), Dulce (sweet, with sugar — distinctive Spanish sweet butter). Distinctive Soriano-region butter tradition.', '**Mantequilla Dulce de Soria** — distinctive sweet butter for breakfast and dessert (with churros, on toast); Natural and Salada for cooking and finishing.', '["plaquette-150g", "plaquette-250g", "jar-Dulce-200g", "professional-bulk-1kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Mantequilla de Soria", "Soria butter"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('c48bc7b6-4c37-7bd2-6396-59164c47986c', 'ES', 'Spain', 'fruits_nuts', 'Espárrago de Navarra IGP', '["Espárrago de Navarra IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Navarran white asparagus IGP, traditional Navarra-Aragón-La Rioja production, mounded-soil cultivation prevents chlorophyll. Bright white spears with tender thick stalks, mildly sweet flavor with delicate vegetal notes — Spain''s most iconic asparagus.', '**Foundation of Navarran cuisine** — Espárragos de Navarra con vinagreta (canonical apéritif), Espárragos con mahonesa, in salads, with jamón; canned premium tier (the most prized format), fresh spring season — pairs with Navarra rosado and Verdejo.', '["fresh-bunch-500g", "fresh-bunch-1kg", "fresh-crate-2.5kg", "jar-glass-180g", "jar-glass-350g", "jar-glass-450g", "can-tin-500g", "gift-pack-jar-180g", "professional-bulk-1kg"]'::jsonb, '[4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Espárrago de Navarra", "Navarran asparagus"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
