  ('9739747f-766a-8332-5cee-aa455e4e0b02', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Volailles de Challans IGP', '["Volailles de Challans IGP", "Canard de Challans IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Vendée Challans-area free-range duck IGP, the iconic French restaurant duck. Lean rich red flesh, distinctive saline-marsh flavor from coastal grazing, firm meaty texture.', '**Magret de canard, confit de canard, foie gras production** (Challans is a major duck-foie gras region); the standard restaurant duck across France; pairs with Madiran, Pinot Noir, Cahors.', '["whole-duck-fresh-1.8-3kg", "eviscerated-vacuum-2-2.5kg", "magret-vacuum-300-400g", "leg-confit-vacuum-200g", "foie-gras-cru-vacuum-500g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Canard de Challans", "Volailles de Challans", "Challans duck", "Vendée duck"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2')
