  ('4242b9dd-9993-5774-51e3-8cd3949c55ca', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Bœuf de Bazas IGP', '["Bœuf de Bazas IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Aquitaine beef from heritage Bazadaise breed. Firm well-marbled meat, robust beefy flavor.', 'Premium south-west beef preparations; pairs with Bordeaux reds (Médoc, Saint-Émilion).', '["Same primal/cut formats as other beef IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Bœuf de Bazas", "Bazadaise beef"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
