  ('b79141c4-23da-806f-255b-61503ba7c716', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Agneau du Poitou-Charentes IGP', '["Agneau du Poitou-Charentes IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Poitou-Charentes lamb IGP.', 'Western France regional lamb preparations.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Agneau du Poitou-Charentes"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('28d2cf24-2f5f-7e91-dbf0-fc5224eb1e46', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Agneau du Quercy IGP', '["Agneau du Quercy IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Quercy lamb IGP from Lot-Tarn-et-Garonne. Causses-region lamb with distinctive grass-fed flavor.', 'South-west regional preparations; pairs with Cahors and Madiran.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Agneau du Quercy"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('e524f500-09c1-c414-ec8c-e9fc379959eb', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Agneau de Pauillac IGP', '["Agneau de Pauillac IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Médoc-Pauillac lamb IGP, traditionally suckled lamb (lait de la mère only). Pale very tender flesh, delicate sweet-mild flavor.', '**Bordeaux luxury restaurant centerpiece** — the canonical pairing with Pauillac AOC red wines (Lafite, Latour, Mouton-Rothschild); served whole or half for special occasions.', '["whole-suckling-lamb-7-10kg", "half-lamb-3.5-5kg", "gigot-1.5-2kg", "côtes-rack-600-800g"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6, 12]'::jsonb, '["Agneau de Pauillac", "Pauillac lamb", "Agneau de lait des Médocs"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('67d730f7-0fdc-92b2-fd8c-5776832a3740', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Agneau de Sisteron IGP', '["Agneau de Sisteron IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Provençal lamb IGP from Alpes-de-Haute-Provence. Lean pink meat with characteristic Provençal-herb-grazed flavor (thyme, rosemary, savory).', '**Provençal restaurant signature** — gigot d''agneau aux herbes; pairs with Côtes-du-Rhône Villages and Bandol.', '["Same as other lamb IGPs"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4, 5, 6]'::jsonb, '["Agneau de Sisteron", "Provençal lamb"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('355e6f19-2929-1037-35fd-49f6ca8c85e0', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Pré-salé du Mont-Saint-Michel AOP', '["Pré-salé du Mont-Saint-Michel AOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Normandy salt-marsh lamb AOP from Mont-Saint-Michel bay. Lean dark-pink meat, distinctively salty-iodized flavor from grazing on salt-marsh halophyte plants (sea-purslane, glasswort), firmer texture than standard lamb. Limited production, premium positioning.', '**Premium Norman/Atlantic restaurant centerpiece** — gigot pré-salé as Norman seasonal specialty; pairs with cidre fermier and Pommard.', '["whole-half-lamb-vacuum-5-7kg", "gigot-1.5-2.5kg", "côtes-rack-600-800g", "épaule-1-1.5kg"]'::jsonb, '[6, 7, 8, 9]'::jsonb, '["Pré-salé du Mont-Saint-Michel", "Agneau de pré-salé", "Salt marsh lamb"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('a213fb26-0dd4-8ce7-5942-add7480115c9', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Prés-salés de la baie de Somme AOP', '["Prés-salés de la baie de Somme AOP"]'::jsonb, 'PDO', '["PDO"]'::jsonb, 'Picardy salt-marsh lamb AOP from Somme bay (Atlantic coast). Similar profile to Mont-Saint-Michel — distinctively salty-iodized flavor from halophyte grazing.', 'Premium Picardy/Norman restaurant centerpiece.', '["Same as Mont-Saint-Michel salt-marsh lamb"]'::jsonb, '[6, 7, 8, 9]'::jsonb, '["Prés-salés de la baie de Somme"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('3e4d47be-f2e7-814e-b480-99e454de366b', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Porc Fermier du Sud-Ouest IGP', '["Porc Fermier du Sud-Ouest IGP", "Porc du Sud-Ouest IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'South-west France free-range pork IGP from heritage breeds. Pink-red meat with golden marbling, robust flavor from chestnut/corn-feed-and-pasture grazing — the foundation pork of cassoulet and south-west cuisine.', 'Cassoulet de Castelnaudary base pork; magret-style preparations; charcuterie processing (jambon de Bayonne, saucisson, etc.); pairs with south-west wines (Madiran, Cahors).', '["carcass-half-40-50kg", "primal-cuts-vacuum-various", "longe-1-2kg", "échine-1kg", "jambon-frais-9-12kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Porc Fermier du Sud-Ouest", "Porc Gascon", "South-west pork"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
