  ('4701aa5e-1a10-8151-0bf0-8977f088cfb9', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Foie gras du Sud-Ouest IGP', '["Foie gras du Sud-Ouest IGP", "Foie gras du Périgord IGP", "Canard à foie gras du Sud-Ouest IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'South-west France goose-and-duck foie gras IGP, the iconic French luxury product. Pale ivory-pink large fatty liver, dense buttery texture, intensely rich savory-fatty flavor with characteristic complexity. Three preparations: foie gras cru (raw, for kitchen processing), foie gras mi-cuit (semi-cooked, ready-to-serve restaurant standard), foie gras conserve (canned, long-aging premium).', '**Premium French restaurant centerpiece** — terrine de foie gras, escalope poêlée, ballotine; on toast pain d''épices; with fig confit and Sauternes-poached pear; **canonical pairing with Sauternes** and other late-harvest sweet wines (Jurançon, Vendange Tardive).', '["cru-vacuum-450-600g", "mi-cuit-terrine-180g", "mi-cuit-terrine-400g", "mi-cuit-tranche-100g", "conserve-tin-180g", "conserve-tin-400g", "gift-pack-200g", "professional-bulk-1.5kg"]'::jsonb, '[11, 12, 1]'::jsonb, '["Foie gras du Sud-Ouest", "Foie gras du Périgord", "Canard à foie gras IGP", "Sud-Ouest foie gras", "Périgord foie gras"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('740961af-4b00-ed3a-cf39-de9630e1e1ef', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Magret de Canard du Sud-Ouest IGP (combined with foie gras IGP)', '["Magret de Canard du Sud-Ouest IGP (combined with foie gras IGP)"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Duck breast from foie gras production (gavage-fed Mulard or Pekin duck). Dark red meat with thick golden-yellow fat cap, firm meaty texture, intensely beefy-savory flavor, characteristic dense fat layer for crispy-rendered service.', '**The iconic south-west restaurant duck dish** — magret de canard pan-seared fat-side-down to crisp; sliced rare-medium with Sauce Périgueux (truffle) or peach/fig glaze; pairs with Madiran, Pacherenc, Cahors.', '["vacuum-pack-300-400g", "vacuum-pack-twin-700g", "frozen-bulk-2kg"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Magret de canard", "Magret du Sud-Ouest"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('8d4e38cd-2a19-b835-9bb4-b6abccb39660', 'FR', 'France', 'cured_meats_charcuterie', 'Confit de canard', '["Confit de canard", "Confit du Sud-Ouest (associated)"]'::jsonb, 'OTHER', '["OTHER", "OTHER"]'::jsonb, 'Salt-cured duck legs slow-cooked and preserved in their own fat, the foundation of cassoulet and south-west cuisine.', 'Cassoulet de Castelnaudary, garbure, salade landaise; pan-fried until crisp-skin for restaurant service; pairs with Madiran.', '["vacuum-pack-2-leg-portion-500g", "tin-confit-2.5kg-bulk", "gift-tin-500g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Confit de canard"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
