  ('856a09ae-4b6e-add5-f799-334273acad1d', 'FR', 'France', 'rice_pasta_grains', 'Pain de Brioche de Vendée IGP', '["Pain de Brioche de Vendée IGP", "Brioche Vendéenne IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI", "PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Vendée plait-shaped enriched bread (eggs, butter, sugar), distinctive three-strand braid. Golden-brown crust, soft tender crumb, sweet egg-rich flavor with subtle eau-de-vie or orange-blossom-water aromatic — Easter and festive bread tradition.', '**Easter brunch service**, with butter and confiture for breakfast, in pain perdu (French toast); paired with Charente-Poitou butter and Confitures Bonne Maman.', '["whole-loaf-300g", "whole-loaf-500g", "whole-loaf-1kg", "gift-pack-500g"]'::jsonb, '[3, 4]'::jsonb, '["Brioche Vendéenne", "Vendée brioche"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
  ('09edd657-6ed7-bf62-1607-c67e20b71343', 'FR', 'France', 'vinegars_condiments', 'Moutarde de Bourgogne IGP', '["Moutarde de Bourgogne IGP"]'::jsonb, 'PGI', '["PGI"]'::jsonb, 'Burgundian mustard IGP, traditional preparation with regional white wine vinegar (Aligoté). Bright golden-yellow paste, smooth texture, balanced sweet-pungent-acidic flavor with characteristic Burgundy character (less aggressive than Dijon, more balanced than American mustards).', '**Foundation of French restaurant condiment service** — with charcuterie and saucisses, in vinaigrettes, sauce moutarde for poulet, in mayonnaise; pairs with Burgundy reds.', '["glass-jar-100g", "glass-jar-200g", "glass-jar-500g", "glass-jar-1kg", "professional-bulk-5kg", "gift-pack-200g"]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '["Moutarde de Bourgogne", "Burgundy mustard"]'::jsonb, FALSE, 'L2'),
